{"tid":1786513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(參考一下對付藍絲老闆) 法國員工不滿低薪　開堆高機輾千台蘋果手機","createTime":"2019-12-17T07:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T08:58:56.000Z","uid":32511,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5438a4f3f05afcc356aafefe04d2f36bd5646a1e","tid":1786513,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"法國普瓦萊市一家手機修理公司的員工，不滿工資過低，員工居然開堆高機到公司門前，當場輾壞1000台蘋果手機，工會代表還說，若資方不接受他們的談判條件，將每天碾壞1000台庫存手機。<br />\n<br />\n抗議現場一名扮成手機模樣的的員工，開著堆高機輾過地上滿滿的蘋果手機。一旁還有不少員工大喊加油。工會表示，如果公司不接受他們的談判條件，每天會繼續輾過1000台庫存手機。報導稱，該公司有2.5萬至3.3萬台蘋果手機庫存，均是回收的二手手機，經修理後將投放市場。<br />\n<br />\n工會表示，目前僅少數員工滿意目前的薪水，並且他們提出的保證工作崗位的計畫，公司也沒有實行。這家公司2014年成立時有680名員工，但9月份被法院勒令重組後，只剩500名員工。"},{"pid":"f8f543cb74a94fade0d744f25e4c3bb51764bdf3","tid":1786513,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a1a697cc373695259ab789c95fcfbc24e50d4c","tid":1786513,"uid":298386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"今晚有香港人道災難哀悼會無人講？！！！！(已有不反)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786309</a><br />\n<br />\n今晩要人啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f56b6cbed6508656aff0fdff